%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20left%20office%20culture%20for%20freelance%20solitude.%20Now%20I%20work%20alone%2C%20wear%20activewear%2C%20and%20earn%20triple.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225146%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch%20with%20a%20laptop%20in%20her%20lap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f4b4ac19ab3675c10910e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223859%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20loves%20working%20from%20home%20because%20she%20enjoys%20the%20solitude.%3Cp%3EMystockimages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20hated%20working%20in%20the%20office%20because%20I%20always%20had%20to%20pretend%20to%20look%20busy%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20trapped.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEight%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20started%20freelancing%20and%20working%20from%20home%20by%20myself%2C%20and%20I%20love%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20enjoy%20the%20solitude%20and%20the%20silence%3B%20plus%2C%20I%20earn%20more%20when%20working%20alone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20went%20freelance%2C%20I%20remember%20sitting%20in%20my%20office%20every%20Friday%20afternoon%20with%20nothing%20to%20do%20because%20I%20finished%20all%20my%20work%20by%2011%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I%20had%20to%20pretend%20to%20work.%20I%20mindlessly%20added%20color-coded%20highlighting%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-excel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20spreadsheet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20beyond%20the%20fluorescent%20lights%2C%20scratchy%20carpets%2C%20and%20drywall%20confines%20lay%20an%20entire%20Friday%20afternoon%20of%20freedom.%20However%2C%20because%20I%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblind-anonymous-tech-job-site-anxiety-layoffs-hiring-ugly-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efull-time%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20only%20started%20at%204%3A30%20p.m.%20Well%2C%204%3A35%20p.m.%2C%20to%20be%20exact%2C%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20look%20like%20I%20was%20clock-watching%20and%20hurrying%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20I%20probably%20had%20a%20good%20laugh%20with%20a%20colleague%2C%20the%20highlight%20of%20my%20day.%20Was%20it%20enough%20to%20make%20up%20for%20an%20entire%20afternoon%20aimlessly%20clicking%20at%20a%20screen%3F%20Not%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20today%2C%20and%20I%20can%20do%20whatever%20I%20want%20with%20my%20Fridays%20because%20I'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-full-time-job-freelance-live-like-early-retiree-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efull-time%20freelancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20work%20alone.%20I%20can%20take%20the%20day%20off%20and%20spend%20it%20with%20my%20actual%20friends%2C%20or%20I%20can%20work%20until%205%3A30%20p.m.%20because%20I'm%20in%20the%20zone%20and%20I%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20you%20get%20lonely%3F%26quot%3B%20It's%20the%20question%20I've%20heard%20roughly%20once%20a%20week%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20years.%20People%20seem%20to%20think%20it's%20the%20price%20of%20admission%20for%20escaping%20corporate%20office%20life%20to%20work%20freelance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20work%20alone%20and%20at%20home%20every%20day.%20Yet%20I've%20never%20been%20happier%20or%20more%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251f76a32-6b50-4fd3-a39d-b22b54c836ed%5C%22%3EFrom%20side%20hustle%20to%20solopreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20good%20millennial%20freelancer%20origin%20stories%2C%20mine%20began%20in%20a%20content%20sweatshop.%20I'd%20clock%20out%20from%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-jobs-mike-krieger-anthropic-entry-level-workers-dario-amodei-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emarketing%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20clock%20in%20to%20%245%20listicles%20that%20evening.%20It%20wasn't%20glamorous%2C%20but%20it%20funded%20my%20social%20life%20and%20taught%20me%20to%20write%20800%20words%20about%20used%20cars%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20listing%3A%20a%20well-paying%2C%20part-time%20freelance%20writing%20gig.%20I%20applied%2C%20mostly%20for%20fun.%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20then%20did%20the%20math%3B%20this%20new%20side%20gig%20paid%20more%20than%20my%20full-time%20salary.%20That%20was%20all%20I%20needed%20to%20go%20full-time%20freelance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20work%20alone%2C%20wear%20activewear%20exclusively%2C%20and%20easily%20earn%20three%20times%20what%20I%20did%20in%20my%20old%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-million-dollar-laundry-business-skills-founders-need-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227e8f9cd-dbd3-4a58-84e2-f89744a85df3%5C%22%3EThe%20truth%20about%20working%20solo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20alone%20isn't%20for%20everyone.%20You%20have%20to%20enjoy%20your%20own%20company%20and%20be%20OK%20commenting%20on%20the%20banal%20details%20of%20the%20weather%20in%20your%20head%20instead%20of%20out%20loud.%20But%20there's%20no%20one%20to%20eat%20boiled%20eggs%20and%20tuna%20next%20to%20me%2C%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-clocks-better-focus-tasks-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclock-watching%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20no%20boss%20to%20ask%20if%20I%20have%20%26quot%3Ba%20sec%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20in%20my%20focus%20zone%2C%20I%20can%20put%20my%20head%20down%2C%20get%20into%20full%20productivity%20mode%2C%20deliver%20my%20best%20work%2C%20and%20smash%20my%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20I'm%20not%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbehaviors-habits-characteristics-of-high-performing-teams-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eteam%20player%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20never%20have%20been.%20Group%20projects%20were%20a%20drag%20in%20school%2C%20and%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20they%20just%20made%20me%20inefficient.%20I'm%20here%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%20possibly%20even%20enjoy%20it%2C%20and%20then%20spend%20guilt-free%20time%20doing%20other%20things%20that%20fill%20my%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20I%20ever%20get%20lonely%3F%20Nope.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20have%20communities%2C%20just%20not%20the%20kind%20that%20involve%20office%20parties%2C%20forced%20fun%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fpassive-aggressive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epassive-aggressive%3C%2Fa%3E%20Post-it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20got%20two%20freelancer%20Facebook%20groups%3A%20one%20local%2C%20one%20global.%20I%20have%20WhatsApp%20threads%20that%20are%20equal%20parts%20client%20rants%20and%20dog%20memes.%20I'm%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Southern%20African%20Freelancers'%20Association.%20And%20I%20meet%20up%20with%20a%20few%20business%20owners%20to%20caffeinate%2C%20commiserate%2C%20and%20occasionally%20co-work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20a%20replacement%20for%20office%20culture%3F%20Hopefully%20not%2C%20because%20I%20left%20that%20behind%20for%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226be25726-13bc-4112-a254-e28136efaacd%5C%22%3EWorking%20alone%20is%20the%20ultimate%20productivity%20hack%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20at%20my%20desk%2C%20there's%20no%20one%20to%20impress%20but%20myself%2C%20no%20one%20to%20interrupt%20the%20flow%2C%20and%20no%20one%20to%20schedule%20a%20%26quot%3Bquick%20touch%20base%26quot%3B%20during%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-lunch-experts-broken-not-take-breaks-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elunch%20break%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20get%20autonomy%2C%20solitude%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20eat%20as%20many%20snacks%20as%20I%20feel%20like%20without%20any%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBest%20of%20all%2C%20I%20actually%20get%20to%20choose%20