ight%3D%5C%222714%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Indiana%20Pacers%20eliminated%20the%20New%20York%20Knicks%20from%20the%20playoffs%20for%20the%20second%20straight%20year%20and%20will%20now%20play%20the%20small-market%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder%20for%20the%20NBA%20title.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Hickey%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFew%20drew%20up%20an%20NBA%20Finals%20between%20the%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder%20and%20the%20Indiana%20Pacers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETV%20ratings%20for%20this%20year's%20championship%20series%20are%20expected%20to%20dip.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20NBA's%20marketing%20team%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20to%20introduce%20new%20superstars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-watch-nba-live-streams%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENBA%20Finals%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20imagined%2C%20but%20the%20league%20sees%20opportunity%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20will%20be%20a%20small-market%20showdown%20between%20the%20mighty%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder%20and%20the%20upstart%20Indiana%20Pacers.%20And%20betting%20markets%20have%20the%20Pacers%20at%205-to-1%20odds%20to%20upset%20the%20Thunder%2C%20who%20won%20a%20staggering%2068%20regular-season%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20combination%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnba-cup-tv-ratings-sports-media-espn-tnt-cord-cutting-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETV%20ratings%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20these%20Finals%20may%20sag.%20Even%20some%20at%20the%20league%20office%20acknowledge%20that%20this%20year's%20Finals%20ratings%20could%20take%20a%20hit%20without%20marquee%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20NBA%20marketing%20chief%20Tammy%20Henault%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20wasn't%20worried%2C%20and%20sees%20the%20series%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20basketball%20stars%2C%20especially%20to%20casual%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20get%20to%20lean%20into%20people%20%E2%80%94%20not%20necessarily%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20Henault%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBA%20hopes%20fans%20will%20fall%20further%20in%20love%20with%20flashy%20young%20stars%20like%20Indiana's%20Tyrese%20Haliburton%20and%20OKC's%20Shai%20Gilgeous-Alexander%2C%20who%20was%20this%20year's%20league%20MVP.%20SGA%2C%20as%20he's%20known%20to%20many%2C%20was%20the%20fourth-most-viewed%20player%20across%20the%20NBA's%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20two%20best%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Patricof%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20sports%20private%20equity%20firm%20Patricof%20Co.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20got%20exciting%20stories%20to%20tell.%20The%20league%20just%20needs%20to%20tell%20their%20stories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Thunder%20are%20heavy%20favorites%20to%20win%20the%20title%2C%20there's%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20Pacers%20can%20keep%20the%20series%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20the%20Pacers%20are%20a%20Cinderella%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bob%20Carney%2C%20the%20NBA's%20head%20of%20social%20and%20digital%20content.%20He%20noted%20that%20these%20two%20squads%20have%20the%20two%20best%20records%20since%20January%201%2C%20including%20the%20playoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220c6d19c-c32b-4257-b82f-190d56b7f3d1%5C%22%3EEmbracing%20unfamiliar%20territory%3A%20Lesser-known%20teams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20would%20love%20to%20see%20the%20New%20York%20Knicks%20face%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Lakers%20every%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20they're%20getting%20Oklahoma%20City%20%E2%80%94%20the%2047th-largest%20US%20TV%20market%20%E2%80%94%20versus%20the%2025th-ranked%20Indianapolis.%20Both%20franchises%20have%20historically%20been%20successful%2C%20but%20neither%20is%20a%20big%20brand.%20And%20household%20names%20like%20LeBron%20James%20and%20Stephen%20Curry%20are%20nowhere%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EESPN%20has%20already%20sold%20the%20ad%20space%20for%20this%20year's%20Finals%2C%20but%20if%20the%20series%20is%20short%20and%20full%20of%20blowouts%2C%20it%20could%20have%20to%20give%20advertisers%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bmake-goods%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20credits%20for%20under-delivered%20ad%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBA%20itself%20is%20largely%20insulated%20from%20a%20ratings%20drop%20because%20it%20signed%20an%2011-year%20media%20rights%20deal%20with%20Disney's%20ESPN%2C%20Comcast's%20NBC%2C%20and%20Amazon%20last%20summer.%20That%20said%2C%20no%20one%20at%20the%20league%20wants%20a%20boring%20series%20that%20people%20tune%20out%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20hasn't%20been%20a%20small-market%20Finals%20matchup%20like%20this%20since%202007%2C%20when%20a%20young%20LeBron%20James%20carried%20the%20undermanned%20Cleveland%20Cavaliers%20to%20face%20the%20juggernaut%20San%20Antonio%20Spurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Carney%20said%20that%20the%20teams'%20market%20size%20doesn't%20impact%20how%20he%20and%20his%20team%20market%20the%20Finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20scrolling%20through%20social%20media%2C%20no%20one's%20thinking%20about%20market%20size%2C%26quot%3B%20Carney%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20be%20entertained.%20They%20want%20to%20talk%20hoops.%20Market%20size%20really%20plays%20no%20role%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EESPN%20also%20isn't%20reinventing%20the%20wheel%20and%20will%20focus%20on%20these%20fast-rising%20teams%20chasing%20their%20first%20titles.%20(The%20Thunder%20moved%20from%20Seattle%2C%20whose%20SuperSonics%20won%20the%201979%20NBA%20title.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224fdd8049-226a-40d1-b5a1-eb1bd1540f8a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20ratings%20bump%20next%20season%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20how%20the%20series%20shakes%20out%2C%20both%20teams%20may%20get%20a%20ratings%20bump%20next%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NBA%20said%20smaller-market%20teams%20have%20garnered%20more%20national%20buzz%20and%20higher%20TV%20ratings%20after%20making%20the%20Finals.%20The%20Milwaukee%20Bucks'%20ratings%20soared%2021%25%20in%20the%20season%20after%20winning%20the%202021%20title%2C%20while%20the%20Denver%20Nuggets%20got%20a%2032%25%20ratings%20boost%20after%20their%202023%20championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20promising%20for%20the%20NBA%2C%20whose%20playoff%20ratings%20have%20risen%203%25%20from%20last%20year%20to%20an%20average%20of%204.5%20million%20viewers%20across%20ABC%2C%20ESPN%2C%20and%20TNT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnba-finals-tv-ratings-indiana-pacers-oklahoma-city-thunder-okc-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749041502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f64699b2a601d01b23ede%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnba-finals-tv-ratings-indiana-pacers-oklahoma-city-thunder-okc-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TV%20ratings%20for%20the%20NBA%20Finals%20with%20the%20Oklahoma%20City%20Thunder%20and%20Indiana%20Pacers%20may%20dip%2C%20but%20the%20NBA's%20marketing%20team%20is%20ready%20to%20highlight%20new%20stars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnba-finals-tv-ratings-indiana-pacers-oklahoma-city-thunder-okc-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chaos%20in%20Bengaluru%3A%20Fans%20climb%20over%20car%2C%20crush%20vehicle%20-%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749041403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121624819%2Cimgsize-4541616.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frcb-celebrations-turn-chaotic-fans-climb-over-car-crush-vehicle-video%2Farticleshow%2F121624