0often%20overlooked%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20waste%20story%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3Ee-waste%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20our%20old%20phones%2C%20broken%20chargers%2C%20defunct%20laptops%2C%20and%20discarded%20appliances%20quietly%20pile%20up.%20While%20they%20may%20seem%20like%20junk%2C%20these%20electronics%20are%20actually%20a%20goldmine%2C%20quite%20literally.%20They%20contain%20valuable%20materials%20like%20copper%2C%20aluminum%2C%20silver%2C%20and%20even%20gold.%20But%20they%20also%20carry%20a%20hidden%20danger.%20Toxic%20substances%20like%20mercury%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20cadmium%20can%20leach%20into%20the%20soil%20and%20water%2C%20harming%20both%20people%20and%20the%20planet%20if%20not%20handled%20correctly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hulladek%20Recycling%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20addressing%20the%20overlooked%20issue%20of%20e-waste%20in%20India%2C%20which%20contains%20valuable%20yet%20hazardous%20materials.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fhulladek-recycling-2-1748957868-768x402.