to-Consumer)%20model%20brings%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F435253%2Fe-waste-disposal-phones-cords-guide-ngo-cpcb%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-waste%20awareness%20%3C%2Fa%3Eright%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps.%20Through%20regular%2C%20door-to-door%20collection%20drives%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20helping%20families%20understand%20what%20e-waste%20really%20is%2C%20why%20it%20matters%2C%20and%20how%20to%20dispose%20of%20it%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20their%20B2B%20(Business-to-Business)%20arm%20supports%20big%20names%20like%20Godrej%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20Mondelez%20International%2C%20and%20Tata%20Steel.%20Hulladek%20handles%20these%20companies%E2%80%99%20e-waste%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20everything%2C%20from%20data%20destruction%20to%20compliance%20with%20government%20norms%2C%20is%20done%20thoroughly%20and%20transparently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20work%20has%20become%20even%20more%20urgent%20with%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1881761%23%3A~%3Atext%3DProducers%2520of%2520notified%2520EEE%252C%2520have%2Cbeyond%2520the%2520maximum%2520prescribed%2520concentration.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20E-Waste%20(Management)%20Rules%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20now%20in%20place.%20These%20rules%20require%20all%20manufacturers%20of%20electronic%20products%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20what%20happens%20to%20their%20products%20after%20use%20%E2%80%94%20a%20principle%20known%20as%20Extended%20Producer%20Responsibility%20(EPR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20companies%20must%20ensure%20their%20e-waste%20is%20being%20collected%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20disposed%20of%20safely%2C%20not%20just%20tossed%20aside.%20The%20law%20also%20sets%20clear%20targets%3A%20by%202023-24%20and%202024-25%2C%2060%25%20of%20e-waste%20generated%20must%