ction%20of%20e-waste%20from%20our%20dedicated%20centres%2C%20the%20materials%20are%20segregated%20and%20sent%20to%20authorised%20recyclers.%20Recycling%20involves%20dismantling%2C%20treating%20hazardous%20components%2C%20and%20segregating%20materials%20into%20categories%20like%20glass%2C%20metal%2C%20and%20plastic%20for%20reuse%20or%20upcycling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20step%20is%20carefully%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20environmental%20standards%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20distinguishes%20us%20from%20informal%20%3Cem%3Ekabadiwala%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(scrap%20dealers)%2C%20who%20are%20often%20confused%20with%20formal%20recyclers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreya%20says%20what%20makes%20Hulladek%20unique%20is%20not%20just%20its%20mission%20but%20its%20workforce%2C%20which%20is%20predominantly%20led%20by%20women.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20an%20average%20employee%20age%20of%2027%2C%20we%20strive%20to%20be%20innovative%20in%20the%20waste%20management%20industry%2C%20and%20our%20gender%20diversity%20is%20unparalleled%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shreya%20beams%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHulladek%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20rooted%20in%20an%20apparent%20belief%3A%20change%20begins%20with%20awareness.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20built%20a%20formidable%20logistics%20network%20backed%20by%20intention%20and%20community%20engagement.%20With%20more%20than%2060%20collection%20centres%20spread%20across%20cities%20like%20Surat%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Agartala%2C%20Hulladek%20conducts%20over%20500%20awareness%20sessions%20each%20year%E2%80%94each%20one%20an%20attempt%20to%20shift%20mindsets%20and%20turn%20passive%20consumers%20into%20conscious%20participants%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20e-waste%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Eastern%20India%2C%20their%20presence%20is%20especially%20significant.%20In%20cities%20like%20Kolkata%2C%20Hulladek%20has%20installed%20nearly%20500%20e-waste%20bins