2C%20and%20that%20price%20was%20always%20paid%20in%20part%20by%20someone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Europe%2C%20they're%20open%20four%20days%20a%20week%2C%20everybody%20knows%20how%20to%20work%20in%20the%20kitchen%20and%20dining%20room%2C%20they%20start%20the%20meal%20earlier%2C%20and%20they're%20closed%20the%20other%20three%20days%20so%20people%20can%20have%20a%20life%20and%20they%20can%20host%20private%20events%20where%20everybody%20can%20make%20extra%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20private%20events%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20in%20the%20form%20of%20special%20dinners%20hosted%20by%20visiting%20chefs%20or%20wineries%20%E2%80%94%20aren't%20just%20great%20for%20additional%20profit.%20They%20bring%20in%20new%20customers%20while%20still%20keeping%20things%20interesting%20for%20the%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lilo%20restuarant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f303b001da6ff18aedfee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFine-dining%20restaurants%20have%20found%20success%20with%20vibrant%20atmospheres%20and%20special%20dinners.%3Cp%3EShelby%20Moore%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegardless%20of%20whether%20we're%20in%20an%20economic%20downturn%20or%20not%2C%20as%20a%20restaurant%2C%20you%20have%20to%20constantly%20be%20evolving%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cimarusti%2C%20who%20is%20hosting%20several%20celebrity-chef%20dinners%20to%20celebrate%20Providence's%2020th%20anniversary%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20guests%20who%20have%20been%20to%20the%20restaurant%20over%20250%20times%20in%2020%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20something%20fresh%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHosting%20special%20dinners%20has%20also%20been%20a%20boon%20for%20Bartolotta's%20restaurants%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20quieter%20weeknights%20and%20chilly%20winter%20months.%20Typically%20ranging%20in%20price%20from%20%2490%20to%20%24250%20per%20person%2C%20the%20dinners%20have%20attracted%20a%20younger%20clientele%20and%20led%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20customer%20base%20for%20The%20Bartolotta%20Restaurants'%20rewards%20program%2C%20which%20offers%20special%20promotions%20and%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20incredible%20how%20many%20people%20we've%20signed%20up%20because%20they%20want%20to%20know%20when%20the%20next%20wine%20dinner%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartolotta%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20program%20has%20%26quot%3Bnorth%20of%2070%2C000%20active%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20found%20similar%20success%20at%20Commander's%20Palace%20after%20her%20team%20encouraged%20her%20to%20create%20a%20tasting%20menu%20inspired%20by%20Taylor%20Swift%20when%20she%20brought%20her%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-facts-earnings-profit-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEras%20Tour%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20New%20Orleans%20in%20October%202024.%20The%20menu%20featured%20dishes%20from%20the%20restaurant's%20famous%20past%20chefs%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femeril-lagasse-facts-celebrity-chef%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmeril%20Lagasse%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20went%20insane%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20never%20sold%20more%20tasting%20menus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestaurateur%20Zimone%20is%20also%20offering%20a%20new%20%2450%20three-course%20tasting%20menu%20at%20Florence%20Osteria%20%26amp%3B%20Piano%20Bar%2C%20which%20he%20opened%20in%20December%202024.%20Zimone%20said%20he%20hopes%20to%20attract%20new%20customers%20after%20his%20business%20dropped%2070%25%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-wildfires-damage-photos-palisades-eaton-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELA%20wildfires%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a483d4f-b9a1-4ae4-896a-abfcbcbe1f10%5C%22%3EEmbrace%20the%20steak%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lilo%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f33d89b2a601d01b236bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20spread%20of%20ingredients%20at%20Lilo%20restaurant.%3Cp%3EShelby%20Moore%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20restaurants%20are%20tweaking%20their%20tasting%20menus%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20offering%20at%20Michelin-starred%20eateries%20%E2%80%94%20others%20aren't%20afraid%20to%20ditch%20them%20entirely%20for%20fresh%20concepts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%3B%20not%20everyone%20can%20afford%20dry-aged%20duck%20with%20cherry%20glaze%2C%26quot%3B%20Meehan%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20dining%20room%20went%20from%20being%20half%20full%2C%20and%20then%20one%20day%20it%20looked%20to%20me%20like%20it%20was%20half%20empty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%2015%20years%20still%20on%20the%20lease%2C%20Meehan%20pivoted%20the%20concept%20of%20Kali%2C%20his%20one-star%20Michelin%20restaurant%2C%20into%20a%20neighborhood%20steakhouse.%20He%20said%20a%20breaking%20point%20was%20when%20the%20Dodgers%20were%20in%20the%20MLB%20playoffs%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20most%20entertaining%20World%20Series%20ever%2C%20so%20every%20night%20for%20about%20a%20month%20we%20were%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20Meehan%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20show%20the%20Dodgers%20game%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20do%20that%20because%20we're%20a%20fancy%20Michelin-star%20restaurant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Kali%2C%20which%20is%20still%20being%20revamped%2C%20will%20have%20a%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20something%20a%20little%20more%20casual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20people%20to%20be%20in%20the%20dining%20room%2C%20talking%20loud%20and%20celebrating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Dodgers%20do%20well%20again%20this%20year%2C%20Meehan%20plans%20to%20give%20out%20free%20%26quot%3BOhtani%20dogs%26quot%3B%20with%20wagyu%20beef%2C%20furikake%2C%20and%20miso%20mustard.%20The%20pared-back%20menu%20will%20also%20feature%20steaks%2C%20classic%20sides%20(shrimp%20cocktails%2C%20wedge%20salads%2C%20potatoes)%2C%20and%20martinis%20that%20Meehan%20hopes%20are%20the%20coldest%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolf%2C%20the%20restaurant%20consultant%2C%20said%20we'll%20likely%20see%20this%20re-embracing%20of%20classic%20dishes%20and%20concepts%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20things%20are%20great%2C%20we'll%20try%20anything.%20When%20things%20are%20tough%2C%20it's%20tried%20and%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20muscle%20comes%20out%20%E2%80%94%20darker%20wood%2C%20heavy%20linens%2C%20a%20slab%20of%20beef.%20It%20just%20makes%20us%20feel%20like%20we're%20getting%20our%20money's%20worth%20and%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20survive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Wolf%20expects%20to%20see%20past%20recession%20indicators%20in%20the%20dining%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20shift%20back%20to%20classic%20French%20restaurants%2C%20historically%20beloved%20and%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2025%2F02%2F18%2Fbusiness%2Fa-french-new-wave-of-chic-restaurants-is-sweeping-nyc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiplying%20again%20in%20NYC%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20he%20thinks%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20fine%20dining%20will%20continue%20to%20evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basis%20of%20the%20vibe%20changes%20with%20the%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20being%20snotty%20to%20people%20is%20not%20the%20vibe%2C%20which%20it%20once%20was.%20Now%2C%20it's%20warm%20and%20welcoming%3B%20the%20true%20luxury%20of%20really