on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%20cabin%20crew%20members%20would%20receive%20pay%20increases%20up%20to%2045.6%25%20over%20the%20contract's%20five-year%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20raise%20would%20be%20as%20much%20as%2027.8%25%2C%20meaning%20a%20rise%20in%20hourly%20pay%20for%20those%20in%20their%20first%20year%20from%20%2428.88%20to%20%2436.92.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20the%20starting%20pay%20would%20be%20%2442.06%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20increases%20for%20longer-serving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflight-attendant-salary-average-delta-american-united-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflight%20attendants%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20between%2026%25%20to%20almost%2028%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20pay%20for%20the%20longest-serving%20staff%20would%20jump%20from%20%2467.11%20an%20hour%20to%20%2484.78.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20contract%2C%20the%20hourly%20rate%20would%20be%20%2496.58.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20attendants%20are%20typically%20only%20paid%20for%20the%20time%20of%20the%20flight%2C%20but%20the%20tentative%20agreement%20also%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-first-airline-to-pay-flight-attendants-for-boarding-union-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehalf-pay%20during%20boarding%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20was%20the%20first%20in%20the%20US%20to%20introduce%20this%20back%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20one-off%20payment%20for%20retroactive%20pay.%20The%20union%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bindustry-leading%26quot%3B%20formula%20worth%20%24595%20million%2C%20which%20compensates%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20cost-of-living%20raise%20for%20United%20flight%20attendants%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContract%20negotiations%20have%20dragged%20on%20while%20competitors%20have%20ratified%20their%20own%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2013%2C%20about%20a%20dozen%20flight%20attendants%20gatecrashed%20a%20press%20event%20unveiling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-new-cabin-polaris-studio-suites-boeing-787-dreamliner-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnited's%20new%20Polaris%20business%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20highlight%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Airlines%20flight%20attendants%20ratified%20a%20deal%20last%20September%20that%20gave%20them%20an%20immediate%20pay%20increase%20of%20up%20to%2020.5%25.%20Five%20months%20earlier%2C%20Southwest%20Airlines%20flight%20attendants%20won%20a%2022.3%25%20pay%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-tells-prospective-flight-attendants-wear-proper-underwear-interviews-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20flight%20attendants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20aren't%20unionized%2C%20have%20received%20annual%20pay%20increases.%20The%20latest%20put%20the%20starting%20wage%20at%20%2436.92%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20as%20United's%20tentative%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20AFA%20is%20set%20to%20hold%20a%20road%20show%2C%20both%20virtually%20and%20at%20airports%20nationwide%2C%20before%20voting%20opens%20on%20July%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoting%20closes%20on%20July%2029.%20If%20the%20contract%20is%20approved%20by%20union%20members%2C%20it%20will%20take%20effect%20the%20following%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpay-rises-united-airlines-flight-attendants-contract-agreement-union-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749037217000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6840202cc19ab3675c109acb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpay-rises-united-airlines-flight-attendants-contract-agre