%20it%20be%20like%2C%20I%20wondered%2C%20to%20be%20an%20MP%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22010816ee-7126-4174-8c75-357c0798d94d%5C%22%3ELeadership%20is%20service%2C%20not%20status%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Ardern%2C%20politics%20was%20never%20about%20prestige.%20Her%20early%20campaign%20work%20taught%20her%20that%20political%20change%20isn%E2%80%99t%20about%20optics%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20election%20wasn't%20just%20something%20that%20was%20battled%20out%20on%20a%20television%20screen.%20It%20wasn't%20about%20phone%20calls%20or%20pages%20of%20an%20Excel%20spreadsheet.%20It%20was%20about%20real%20things%20that%20happened%20to%20real%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3684a2c-e9cd-4382-941e-2d4b8019d532%5C%22%3EEmpathy%20is%20not%20weakness%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMocked%20and%20jeered%20in%20Parliament%20as%20a%20young%20MP%2C%20Ardern%20wondered%20if%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20thin-skinned%20for%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20party%20veteran%20urged%20her%20not%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPromise%20me%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20try%20to%20toughen%20up%2C%20Jacinda.%20You%20feel%20things%20because%20you%20have%20empathy%20and%20because%20you%20care.%20The%20moment%20you%20change%20that%20is%20the%20moment%20you%E2%80%99ll%20stop%20being%20good%20at%20your%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee3a9c69-8ad9-452f-bd05-05c85e10230b%5C%22%3EThe%20traits%20you%20think%20disqualify%20you%20may%20be%20what%20make%20you%20a%20great%20leader%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJacinda%20Ardern%20often%20felt%20she%20didn't%20fit%20the%20mold%20of%20a%20traditional%20politician%20%E2%80%94%20too%20anxious%2C%20too%20empathetic%2C%20too%20filled%20with%20self-doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20time%2C%20she%20learned%20to%20see%20those%20traits%20as%20assets%2C%20not%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20impostor%20syndrome%20o