t%20rifles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Polish%20paratrooper%20holds%20his%20MSBS%20Grot%20during%20the%20Lively%20Sabre%2025%20exercise%20in%20Finland%20in%20May.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683eff286ffb6822ec61f2f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPoland's%206th%20Airborne%20Brigade%20is%20armed%20with%20the%20locally%20made%20MSBS%20Grot.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPoland's%206th%20Airborne%20Brigade%20has%20been%20using%20the%20MSBS%20Grot%20assault%20rifle%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20gun%2C%20designed%20by%20a%20Polish%20arms%20maker%2C%20comes%20with%20a%20retractable%20or%20adjustable%20folding%20stock.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20makes%20it%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20paratroopers%2C%20a%20Polish%20captain%20told%20BI%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20rifle%20are%20elite%20Polish%20paratroopers%20jumping%20into%20combat%20with%3F%20A%20relatively%20new%20homemade%20gun%20that%20they%20say%20offers%20flexibility%20and%20mobility%20needed%20at%20a%20time%20when%20modern%20warfare%20is%20showing%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-shows-polish-paratroopers-light-infantry-skills-matter-general-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elight%20infantry%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20key%20part%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoland's%206th%20Airborne%20Brigade%20previously%20carried%20the%2096%20Beryl%2C%20a%20rifle%20developed%20by%20the%20Polish%20firearms%20manufacturer%20FB%20Radom%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20brigade%20is%20fully%20armed%20with%20FB%20Radom's%20newer%20MSBS%20Grot%2C%20a%20family%20of%20modular%20rifles.%20The%20gun's%20stock%20can%20be%20folded%20or%20retracted%2C%20making%20it%20compact%20and%20%26quot%3Bgood%20for%20the%20jump%2C%26quot%3B%20Capt.%20Bartosz%20Januszewski%20told%20Business%20Insider%20during%20the%20Lively%20Sabre%2025%20exercise%20in%20southern%20Finland%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompact%20weapons%20are%20often%20preferred%20by%20airborne%20forces%20and%20mechanized%20infantry%20because%20they%20allow%20troops%20to%20move%20more%20freely%20in%20confined%20spaces%2C%20deploy%20more%20rapidly%2C%20and%20react%20quickly.%20They%20can%20be%20carried%20close%20to%20the%20body%20to%20avoid%20snags%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20swiftly%20extended%20and%20shouldered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJanuszewski%20said%20the%20airborne%20brigade%20received%20the%20first%20MSBS%20Grot%20model%20in%202017.%20Some%20of%20the%206th%20Airborne%20are%20now%20using%20the%20third%20model%2C%20which%20was%20handed%20over%20in%202022%2C%20and%20new%20variations%20are%20still%20being%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20manufacturer%2C%20the%20MSBS%20Grot%20fires%20standard%205.56%C3%9745mm%20NATO%20cartridges%20and%20has%20a%20muzzle%20velocity%20of%20890%20meters%20per%20second.%20It%20can%20shoot%20between%20700%20and%20900%20rounds%20a%20minute%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%20500%20meters.%20The%20gun%20weighs%20around%204%20kilograms%20(under%209%20pounds)%20and%20is%20just%20shy%20of%201%2C000%20mm%20(38%20inches)%20long%20with%20the%20weapon's%20stock%20fully%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225705%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Polish%20soldiers%20hold%20the%20FB%20Radom%20MSBS%20Grot%20in%20April%202022%20in%20Gdynia%2C%20Poland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683eff97c6ad288d14825fd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223803%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20MSBS%20Grot%20is%20made%20by%20the%20Polish%20defense%20manufacturer%20FB%20Radom.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Michal%20Fludra%2FNurPhoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20paratroopers%20employ%20holographic%20weapons%20sights%20made%20by%20the%20US%20company%20EOTech.%20The%20gun%20can%20also%20be%20equipped%20with%20magnifier%20attachments%20and%20infrared%20lights%20for%20night%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJanuszewski%20said%20that%20Poland%20prefers%20to%20use%20homemade%20rifles%20rather%20than%20purchase%20them%20from%20another%20country%2C%20like%20the%20US%2C%20because%20it%20helps%20grow%20the%20local%20defense%20industry.%20It%20also%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20liaise%20directly%20with%20the%20company%20to%20share%20feedback%20and%20discuss%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrig.%20Gen.%20Michal%20Strzelecki%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Poland's%206th%20Airborne%20Brigade%2C%20told%20BI%20during%20Lively%20Sabre%20that%20not%20all%20units%20in%20the%20Polish%20Army%20use%20the%20MSBS%20Grot.%20However%2C%20his%20paratroopers%20tend%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20newer%20weapons%20systems%20earlier%20than%20others%20across%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20some%20critics%20have%20complained%20about%20issues%20like%20jamming%2C%20the%20general%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%20rifle%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he's%20%26quot%3Bquite%20satisfied%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20weapon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Staff%20Sergeant%20in%20the%206th%20Airborne%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20exercise%20and%20spoke%20to%20BI%20through%20a%20translator%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20said%20the%20MSBS%20Grot%20is%20better%20than%20the%20Kalashnikov-style%20Beryl%20he%20was%20using%20earlier%20in%20his%20career.%20He%20characterized%20the%20new%20rifle%20as%20being%20very%20user-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20earlier%20Beryls%2C%20the%20Grot%20offers%20a%20more%20modern%2C%20adaptable%2C%20and%20modular%20rifle%20that%20Poland%20felt%20better%20met%20the%20demands%20of%2021st-century%20warfare%20than%20Soviet-derived%20designs.%20It%20also%20strengthened%20the%20domestic%20defense%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MSBS%20Grot%20is%20primarily%20used%20by%20Polish%20forces%2C%20but%20Warsaw%20has%20sent%20thousands%20of%20these%20rifles%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideos-ukrainian-strikes-on-russian-aircraft-shielded-by-tires-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20its%20neighbor%20fend%20off%20the%20ongoing%20Russian%20invasion.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguns-grenades-candy-ukraine-fighter-describes-his-military-gear-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eforeign%20volunteer%3C%2Fa%3E%20BI%20spoke%20to%20earlier%20this%20year%20previously%20said%20he's%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20fan%20of%20the%20Grot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-polish-paratroopers-like-homemade-grot-rifles-for-air-jumps-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749031621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683eff286ffb6822ec61f2f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-polish-paratroopers-like-homemade-grot-rifles-for-air-jumps-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20MSBS%20Grot%2C%20a%20family%20of%20modular%20rifles%20made%20by%20Poland's%20FB%20Radom%2C%20has%20features%20that%20make%20it%20%26quot%3Bgood%20for%20the%20jump%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20officer%20told%20BI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-polish-paratroopers-like-homemade-grot-rifles-for-air-jumps-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhishek%20told%20Aalim%3A%20'I'll%20put%20a%20bullet%20in%20your%20leg'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749031587000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121620709%2Cimgsize-79464.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2