%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPhase%202%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%2C%20however%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20over.%20unTAG%20has%20already%20completed%20the%20design%20for%20Phase%20two%2C%20which%20includes%20expanding%20the%20school%20to%20accommodate%20skill-based%20education%20for%20Classes%2011%20and%2012%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy.%20The%20team%20is%20now%20actively%20seeking%20donors%20and%20partners%20to%20help%20realise%20this%20next%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20just%20about%20one%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejesh.%20%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20replicable%20model%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ecosystem%20of%20rural%20schools%20that%20are%20sustainable%2C%20beautiful%2C%20and%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20their%20context.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Gauri%20and%20Tejesh%2C%20who%20both%20have%20rural%20connections%2C%20the%20project%20is%20personal.%20It%20is%20a%20fusion%20of%20passion%20and%20profession%2C%20a%20belief%20that%20good%20design%20should%20be%20accessible%2C%20that%20architecture%20can%20be%20an%20agent%20of%20social%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20every%20building%20should%20resonate%20with%20its%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gauri%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20every%20child%20deserves%20to%20learn%20in%20a%20space%20that%20respects%20their%20identity%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Saraswati%20Vidyalaya%2C%20that%20vision%20has%20taken%20root%20%E2%80%94%20brick%20by%20brick%2C%20with%20care%2C%20consciousness%2C%20and%20community%20at%20its%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20credit%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.untagarchitecture.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EunTAG%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748766600000%2C%22visual%22